  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "folder": "fhSubSciFi000001",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A single-use transdermal patch favored by dock crews working triple shifts. The active blend kicks in within seconds; the comedown is shorter and meaner than the high. Approved for spaceport use only on paper; in practice it follows the freight.</p><p><strong><em>Desired effects on use.</em></strong> For 30 minutes you ignore the effects of one level of exhaustion and have advantage on Constitution checks made to stay awake.</p><p><strong><em>On use, save against addiction.</em></strong> Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, you gain the Addicted condition from Spaceport Stim-Patch (see below).</p><p><strong><em>Addicted from Spaceport Stim-Patch.</em></strong> While you have this Addicted condition, you are also Poisoned and have disadvantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on hearing (a faint ringing in your ears).</p><p><strong><em>Withdrawal Modifier: 3.</em></strong> Withdrawal lasts max(3 &minus; your Constitution modifier, 2) long rests, minimum 1.</p><p><em>Requires: Dermal Applicator.</em></p>"
    },
